text: Isaan sun warra dogoggora xixiqqoo malee dilii gugurdoofi sagaagalummaa irraa fagaataniidhaDhugumatti, Gooftaan kee araaramni Isaa balâ€™aadhaInni yeroo dachii irraa isin uumeefi yeroo isin garaa haadha keessanii keessatti ulfa taatanii jirtan akkaan isin beekaLubbuu keessan hin qulqulleessinaaInni nama (Isa) sodaatu akkaan beekaadha
